headline: Duke Energy captures nine awards at acclaimed international lineworker rodeo competition
summary: Duke Energy teams brought home nine awards over the weekend after competing in one of the most celebrated lineworker competitions in the world – the International Lineman's Rodeo – on Oct. 18 in Bonner Springs, Kansas.

headline: PG&E to Report Q3 Earnings: What's in the Cards for the Stock?
summary: PCG's third-quarter results are likely to benefit from stronger sales, lower costs and new clean-energy initiatives despite mixed weather impacts.
